48
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:42,000
Ese desgraciado tonto de este mundo.

49
00:07:43,458 --> 00:07:45,166
Suena duro.

50
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:47,583
¿Eres soltero?

51
00:07:48,500 --> 00:07:50,666
