222
00:21:32,041 --> 00:21:33,208
Guau.

223
00:21:34,583 --> 00:21:35,833
Hermoso.

224
00:21:37,208 --> 00:21:38,208
Sí.

225
00:21:43,750 --> 00:21:44,666
Ey.

226
00:21:45,375 --> 00:21:47,958
